<A>__{lhamo elbows his brother. lobsang elbows him back. the two begin to squabble.}
<C>__{lhamo}
<D>__{you have all the room.}
<C>__{lobsang}
<D>__{don't be a baby, move over.}
<C>__{lhamo}
<D>__{you move.}
<C>__{lobsang}
<D>__{you! you think you are so big!}
<A>__{they hit and pinch until finally the movement of the carriage stops. the driver reaches in through the open curtains and separates the boys, each to his own side of the dreljam. inside his tiny carriage, young lhamo now sits quiet and composed.}
